duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide financial products and services, and education to teachers, school administrators, and municipality employees.
Attain state life and health licenses, SIE, FINRA Series 7 and 66 exams (other designations a plus).
Develop markets and sustain long-term relationships by drawing upon past/present experiences and acquaintances.
Sponsorship and coaching to obtain the licensing required for hire.

education_certification.credential: Four-year college degree preferred but not required.
